Cyber Security
Cyber security would be a major concern for a voting system. Fortunately in this case, there is no risk of an attacker changing a vote or submitting fraudulent votes into the system. However one concerning area is that an attacker might find a way to see which way the voters are voting.

While the area of concern is different compared to most e-Voting systems, it is still a serious concern as well functioning democratic system can only exist where votes are anonymous.




